  <dashboards>
    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Q1 - Quality Trends'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='1300' maxwidth='1200' minheight='1300' minwidth='1200' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98154' id='24' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98000' x='1000' y='923'>
            <zone h='98154' id='19' type-v2='layout-basic' w='98000' x='1000' y='923'>
              <zone h='64154' id='10' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98000' x='1000' y='923'>
                <zone h='64154' id='8' type-v2='layout-basic' w='98000' x='1000' y='923'>
                  <zone forceUpdate='true' h='9963' id='3' type-v2='text' w='98000' x='1000' y='923'>
                    <formatted-text>
                      <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='16'>Lead Quality is Declining - Driven by Audience Mix Changes, Not Lead Source Quality</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='14'>Æ </run>
                      <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Q1: Are we seeing any lead quality trends over time? </run>
                      <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                      <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Are they statistically significant?</run>
                    </formatted-text>
                    <zone-style>
                      <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                      <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                      <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                      <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                      <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                    </zone-style>
                  </zone>
                  <zone h='54191' id='5' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98000' x='1000' y='10886'>
                    <zone fixed-size='679' h='54191' id='22' is-fixed='true' name='Monthly Trend' w='57250' x='1000' y='10886'>
                      <layout-cache type-h='fixed' type-w='cell' />
                      <zone-style>
                        <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                        <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                        <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                        <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                      </zone-style>
                    </zone>
                    <zone h='54191' id='6' name='DQ Surge' w='40750' x='58250' y='10886'>
                      <layout-cache minwidth='173' type-h='fixed' type-w='scalable' />
                      <zone-style>
                        <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                        <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                        <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                        <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                        <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                      </zone-style>
                    </zone>
                  </zone>
                </zone>
              </zone>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='34000' id='12' type-v2='text' w='98000' x='1000' y='65077'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>FINDINGS</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>1. Lead quality is declining over time, with conversion dropping from 10.8% (April) to 4.4% (September). </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>2. This decline is statistically significant (p = 0.008), confirming it is not due to random variation. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>3. The primary driver is a shift in audience composition toward lower-quality users. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>4. Users with less than $10K debt increased from 0% to 22% and convert at ~5%. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>5. High-performing creatives were removed and replaced with lower-performing ones. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>6. Traffic shifted toward Google, replacing higher-converting partners. </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>7. Contactability improved (8.1% to 3.8%), so lead validity is not the issue </run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>8. Overall, the decline is driven by targeting and campaign mix changes.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='12' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
