    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Q3 - Optimisation'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='1300' maxwidth='1200' minheight='1300' minwidth='1200' sizing-mode='fixed' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='64462' id='9' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98000' x='1000' y='923'>
            <zone h='64462' id='7' type-v2='layout-basic' w='98000' x='1000' y='923'>
              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='11292' id='3' type-v2='text' w='98000' x='1000' y='923'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='16'>Two Paths to 9.6%+ Conversion - Both Using Standard Campaign Optimization</run>
                  <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='16'>Æ </run>
                  <run fontalignment='1'>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontalignment='1' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Q3: If the advertiser increases CPL by 20% for a 20% quality increase, do we see opportunities to do that?</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                  <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
              <zone h='53170' id='5' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98000' x='1000' y='12215'>
                <zone fixed-size='550' h='53170' id='11' is-fixed='true' name='Creative Rotation' w='46500' x='1000' y='12215'>
                  <layout-cache type-h='fixed' type-w='cell' />
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
                <zone h='53170' id='6' name='Google Campaigns' w='51500' x='47500' y='12215'>
                  <layout-cache minwidth='256' type-h='fixed' type-w='scalable' />
                  <zone-style>
                    <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                    <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                    <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                    <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                    <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
                  </zone-style>
                </zone>
              </zone>
            </zone>
          </zone>
          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='33692' id='13' type-v2='text' w='98000' x='1000' y='65385'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>RECOMMENDED PATHS</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>A 20% improvement in conversion (8.0% to 9.6%) is achievable through focused optimization. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>This can be achieved by focusing on higher-quality segments and optimizing campaigns.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>Path 1: </run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>Target users with $10K - $100K debt and remove low-performing creatives. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>This increases conversion to 9.6% with ~47% reduction in volume. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>Path 2: </run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>Reallocate budget from low-performing to high-performing Google campaign. </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>Pause “DebtReductionInc” (4.0%) and invest in “Debt Holding Tank” (14.5%). </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>This increases conversion to 10.3% with ~50% reduction in volume.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>Additional recommendation:</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'> Introduce tiered CPL pricing to align incentives with incremental quality improvements.  </run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='12'>Overall, improving lead quality requires prioritizing efficiency and targeting precision over scale.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
              <format attr='margin' value='4' />
              <format attr='background-color' value='#ffffff' />
            </zone-style>
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='12' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
